data.description: PRICE REDUCED! This custom all brick and stone house has room for everyone with 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, oversized 3 car garage and a little over 2 acres. If that's not enough, this home has a beautiful view and a cleared trail right down to the beautiful useable shoreline of Table Rock Lake! Yep.....that's right, WALK to the lake (or take the Kawasaki Mule 4070 - included with the home) AND LAKEVIEW! The inside of the home is just as immaculate as the outside. Some of the interior highlights include all granite counters with custom cabinetry throughout, wood burning fireplace with plenty of cut firewood, all upgraded appliances, large master bedroom with spacious master bathroom, and so much more! This home also has a fully finished walk out basement with large rec room and fully wired in media and kitchenette with LG appliances, large John Deer room currently used as an exercise room and two spacious bedrooms. This home has all new custom paint inside and out, has a new roof in 2021, new luxury carpet, new landscaping and fencing, new propane plumbed into the kitchen and outdoor BBQ area with a 100 gallon tank, new well pump, new smart water softener, new smart thermostat, and so much more. This home could possibly be a nightly rental as it previously was used as one - you'd have to check with Stone county to be sure though. Both decks have amazing views of Table Rock Lake at Point 7 in Kimberling City all year round. Lastly, there is RV parking and exterior hookups for septic & electric and plenty of space to park a boat. The location is perfect - enjoy the peace and quiet yet you're only 5 miles from Kimberling City, shopping, dining and the Port of Kimberling. There are several boat docks very close to possibly purchase a slip from a third party when one comes available. This is the PERFECT lake home - DON'T MISS IT!!
